<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818325>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Collection localities of Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. Type locality is indicated by a star." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818325/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818329>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. in life. (A) Male holotype VNMN 2016 A. 22 and male paratypes (B) AMS R 184852, (C) AMS R 184851, (D) VNMN 2016 A. 26." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818329/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818333>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Ventral, dorsal and lateral views of (A) male holotype (VNMN 2016 A. 22) and (B) female paratype (VNMN 2016 A. 21) of Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. in preserve. Note difference in ventral colouration between sexes. Scale bars = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818333/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818331>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ventral and dorsal views of (A) male holotype (VNMN 2016 A. 22) and (B) female paratype (VNMN 2016 A. 21) of Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. showing colour in life. Note difference in ventral colouration between sexes. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818335>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Advertisement call of Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. (A) 30 s waveform of relative amplitude (Rel. amp.) over time for (i) holotype VNMN 2016 A. 22, (ii) paratype NCSM 79649, (iii) paratype VNMN 2016 A. 26, and (iv) paratype AMS R 184852. (B) 2 s waveform and corresponding spectrogram of (i – ii) holotype VNMN 2016 A. 22, (iii – iv) paratype NCSM 79649, (iv – v) paratype VNMN 2016 A. 26, and (vi – vii) AMS R 184852. All recorded at 22.3 – 25.8 ° C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818335/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.818337>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. (A – B) Breeding habitat of Leptolalax puhoatensis sp. nov. and (C) deforestation in Pu Hoat Nature Reserve, Nghe An Province, Vietnam." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/818337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

